  "2111660": {
    "name": "Rock Paper SMASH",
    "steam_appid": 2111660,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rock Paper SMASH</strong> is a unique spin on the platform fighter genre combining strategy, chaos, and humor. Anyone from seasoned veteran to complete novice can have a blast with the core mechanic: the only attack options are Rock, Paper, Scissors. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featuring</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Support for your favorite classic controllers and controller adapters</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online multiplayer with <strong>Rollback Netcode</strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A hilarious single player adventure</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;Duel mode&quot;: a pure rock-paper-scissors battle of wits with trickery and taunts</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>While the core attacks are always Rock Paper Scissors, all characters feel unique and add their own distinct flavor to the game. Meet some of the iconic cast:</i></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FRIDGE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111660/extras/64fc2210d8a1ef1b43d9235283bccc97.poster.avif?t=1755367265\" width=608 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111660/extras/64fc2210d8a1ef1b43d9235283bccc97.webm?t=1755367265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111660/extras/64fc2210d8a1ef1b43d9235283bccc97.mp4?t=1755367265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Big and very slow, but get too close and you're toast. Fridge has huge attacks with huge damage. Holding the jump button allows Fridge to slowly blast-off like a rocket.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>MARK  </strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111660/extras/65349f808ceca34458184d0b165c7515.poster.avif?t=1755367265\" width=608 height=148 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111660/extras/65349f808ceca34458184d0b165c7515.webm?t=1755367265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111660/extras/65349f808ceca34458184d0b165c7515.mp4?t=1755367265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mark boasts disjointed sword attacks and has unique movements when attacking; Scissors performs a forward dash, Paper is akin to an extra jump with an uppercut motion, and Rock does a downward fast falling dive.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><br>CAR</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111660/extras/de7eae17653581e4ef3131142d5244e1.poster.avif?t=1755367265\" width=608 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111660/extras/de7eae17653581e4ef3131142d5244e1.webm?t=1755367265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111660/extras/de7eae17653581e4ef3131142d5244e1.mp4?t=1755367265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Heavy but with super fast movement speed, Car can follow up on attacks that others can't. Jumping with Car creates a physics-based ramp which works based on how fast you're moving.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>  </strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FOX</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111660/extras/55460880eb1df3270263d12a345512ce.poster.avif?t=1755367265\" width=608 height=134 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111660/extras/55460880eb1df3270263d12a345512ce.webm?t=1755367265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111660/extras/55460880eb1df3270263d12a345512ce.mp4?t=1755367265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Having both photo-realistic and cartoon skins, Fox attacks quickly enough to keep anyone on their toes. Fox is sure to distract everyone with his shiny blue taunt!<strong></strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>And many more ... </i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> Taunting with Rock-Paper-Scissors</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Taunting is an important part of any fighting game. Rock Paper SMASH features a normal taunt on each character, <strong>but also every character can do a &quot;Rock&quot; &quot;Paper&quot; or &quot;Scissors&quot; taunt</strong> for added mind-games and tricks. Tell your opponent <i><strong>&quot;I'm going to rock&quot;</strong></i> repeatedly, then, maybe... still go <strong>Rock</strong>!<strong>  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111660/extras/1b59c577f513a1239607a0684e804c6a.poster.avif?t=1755367265\" width=608 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111660/extras/1b59c577f513a1239607a0684e804c6a.webm?t=1755367265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111660/extras/1b59c577f513a1239607a0684e804c6a.mp4?t=1755367265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
